&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a new colleague to join our Cardiology team at the Royal Devon and Exeter Hospital. Due to a retirement, the post is offered on a part-time basis - currently 5-6 PAs. We are a forward thinking group of doctors working in an ambitious and dynamic department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Come and join a young team of enthusiastic doctors, we mostly have young families and promote part time working plus diverse portfolios to make our jobs sustainable. South East Devon is a great place to live and bring up a family. We have outdoor appeal with our beautiful national parks and coastline. Exeter polls highly in the UK’s best places to live and is well connected by road, rail and air.&lt;/p&gt;
